README - EnvironmentStatistics (EnvironmentStatistics Plugin)
================================

EnvironmentStatistics is a plugin to allow the user adds a block where you could see statistics of the environment.

The EnvironmentStatistics block will be available for all layout columns of communities, peole, enterprises and environments.

INSTALL
=======

Enable Plugin
-------------

Also, you need to enable EnvironmentStatistics Plugin at you Noosfero:

cd <your_noosfero_dir>
./script/noosfero-plugins enable environment_statistics

Active Plugin
-------------

As a Noosfero administrator user, go to administrator panel:

- Click on "Enable/disable plugins" option
- Click on "Environment Statistics Plugin" check-box

DEVELOPMENT
===========

Get the Environment Statistics (Noosfero with Environment Statistics Plugin) development repository:

$ git clone https://gitorious.org/+noosfero/noosfero/environment_statistics

Running EnvironmentStatistics tests
--------------------

$ rake test:noosfero_plugins:environment_statistics


Get Involved
============

If you found any bug and/or want to collaborate, please send an e-mail to eduardo.edington@gmail.com

